  <p style="font-size: 23px;">It is simple.</p>
  <p style="color: rgb(54, 54, 165);">1. Givers and Takers - Create an account in this web application and Login.</p>
  <p style="color: rgb(54, 54, 165);">2. Givers - Please take a photo of your item you want to donate. Please attach the photo while raising the pickup request. Once any taker shows interest, please communicate with the taker.</p>
  <p style="color: rgb(54, 54, 165);">3. Takers - Please search based on your location. If you find your required item, please contact the giver and schedule for pickup.</p>
  <p style="color: rgb(54, 54, 165);">4. Givers - Once item is donated to the takers, please discard the pickup request so that the pickup request is no longer visible to others.</p>
  
